      "value": "<p>Granted by @UUID[Compendium.immortal-ardor.classes.ZUuTE44cpQWVu4k3]{Scalekin Zenith}</p><p>Tiny ethereal dragon spirits adds damage or hit points to your next damaging or healing effect. This applies to only a single target per instance of damage at a time, and one spirit disappears. <span lang=\"EN\" style=\"box-sizing:border-box;user-select:text;scrollbar-width:initial;scrollbar-color:initial\"><span style=\"font-family:Roboto, sans-serif\">A dragon can only add this benefit for one triggering effect at a time. The number of dragons you summon is equal to the amount of Zeal you spend. The Zenith ends after 1 minute, or when all dragons have disappeared.</span></span></p>"
